Package com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.validationMethod

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractValidationMethod
    The abstract class for every response item that specifies how to validate the AbstractValidationMethod.expressionToValidate.
    CountValidator
    Validates that AbstractValidationMethod.getExpressionToValidate() has the size of the Integer value of CountValidator.count.
    CountValidatorTest
    Tests CountValidator
    ExistsValidator
    Validates that AbstractValidationMethod.getExpressionToValidate() is neither null nor empty.
    ExistsValidatorTest
    Tests ExistsValidator
    MatchesValidator
    Validates that the first result in AbstractValidationMethod.getExpressionToValidate() matches the Pattern provided by MatchesValidator.validationExpression.
    MatchesValidatorTest
    Tests MatchesValidator
    TextValidator
    Validates that the first result in AbstractValidationMethod.getExpressionToValidate() equals TextValidator.validationExpression.
    TextValidatorTest
    Tests TextValidator
    ValidationMethodTest
    Prepares AbstractValidationMethod tests by creating a new context
